  <brief_title>Coadministration of Ezetimibe With Fenofibrate Versus Pravastatin Monotherapy for the Treatment of Hyperlipidaemia in HIV-infected Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Coadministration of Ezetimibe With Fenofibrate Versus Pravastatin Monotherapy for the Treatment of Hyperlipidaemia in HIV-infected Patients Receiving Protease Inhibitors: a Randomized, Prospective, Controlled Pilot Study.</official_title>
